premise_source_doc_sentence: Johan Heldenbergh  (  born 9 February 1967  )  is a Belgian actor , playwright , screenwriter , theatre director and film director .

He gained international fame by starring in films such as A Day in a Life  (  2007  )  , Moscow , Belgium  (  2008  )  , The Misfortunates  (  2009  )  and The Broken Circle Breakdown  (  2012  )  , as well The Zookeepers Wife  (  2017  )
